Class Products

java.lang.Object
com.example.Products
public class Products extends Object
The Products class is a container for a product a customer might order from the boba store. It has all of the properties of a menu item
Author:
Licheng Yi

  • Constructor Details

    • Products

      public Products(String name, double price, int id, int category, int qty)
      This is the constructor for a product
      Parameters:
      name - is the name of the product
      price - is the price of the product (excluding tax)
      id - is the id of the product stored in the database
      category - is the category the product belongs in (stored in the databse)
      qty - is the number of current stock we have of that particular product
